room_title: Escape room "The Fun House" by Cross Roads Escape Games in Los Angeles
room_address: 4245 E La Palma Ave, Anaheim, CA 92807
room_description: Do you have the wits to become the magician's apprentice? Or are you a clueless clown? Come and test your skill to see if you have what it takes to look past all the tricks and illusions in this crazy, fun, and upside-down game!
